  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>macaroni</strong> for 6-7 min or until cooked with a bite</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>chopped basil</strong> and<strong> chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!)<strong> </strong>in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>bruschetta mix</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once ready, drain the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>macaroni</strong> and reserve 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and set aside until later, reserve the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated cheese </strong>with your <strong>cornflour</strong> – this is your <strong>coated cheese</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>coated cheese</strong>,<strong> soft cheese </strong>and<strong> </strong>90ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[135ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[180ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>to the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong> – this is your<strong> cheese sauce mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with your <strong>plant based 'Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cheese sauce mix</strong> to the pot with a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cooked macaroni </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains – this is your <strong>mac 'n' cheese mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese mix</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(use individual ones for fancy presentation!), top with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>veggie 'Nduja mac 'n' cheese</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced ciabatta </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for an initial 6 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 6 min, remove the tray with the ciabatta from the oven</p><p>Add your <strong>pine nuts </strong>to the other side of the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 4 min or until the pine nuts are toasted  – this is your <strong>toasted ciabatta & pine nuts</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-veggie-nduja-mac-n-cheese-with-bruschetta/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>toasted ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>bruschetta mix </strong>– this is your<strong> bruschetta</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>veggie 'Nduja mac 'n' cheese </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
